posting_body: ['Apartments with convenience and serenity, nestled in a peaceful, park-like setting.', 'Nestled in a peaceful, park-like setting, James Apartments offers renovated one, two and three bedroom apartments in Lakewood, WA.', 'Experience convenience and the serenity of our community as we are off the beaten path yet close to everything:', 'Clover Park Tech, Pierce County Sounder, Bates Tech, Gravelly Lake, St Clare Hospital, Lakewood Gardens and Lakewood Towne Center, fine dining and specialty shops.', 'James is about 3 miles from the entrance of the former McChord Airforce base (now JBLM) and 8 miles from the main gates of former Ft.', 'Lewis (JBLM).', 'Take a dip in our heated outdoor pool or exercise in our exclusive get fit gym.', 'Welcome home!', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 33', 'OR Text', '33', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our leasing team.', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 700 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Package Receiving', '- Balcony*', '- Range', '- Individual Climate Control', '- Washer and Dryer*', '- Large Closets', '- Window Coverings', '- Dishwasher*', '- Private Patio*', '*Select Units', 'Community Amenities', '- 24-Hour Availability', '- On-site Management', '- State-of-the-Art Fitness Center', '- Cyber Café', '- On-site Maintenance', '- Courtyard', '- Pool With Sundeck', '- Clubhouse', '- Disability Access', '- Freeway Access', '- Internet Access: High Speed', '- Accepts Credit Card Payments', '- Concierge Services', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'James Apartments', '4828 123rd St SW, Lakewood, WA, 98499', 'LrxpXC26v']
